entries.s_13: He could be anywhere!! Oh, he likes to play at the shuttleports and watch the shuttles come and go. And he loves the bridge between the two parts of the city. Maybe he's in one of those locations.
entries.s_14: I'll go see if he's there.
entries.s_15: I'll wait here in case he returns on his own. Thank you for helping me!
entries.s_16: You found Peaches!! Thank you, thank you, thank you!!!
entries.s_18: I can't find my pet durni! Peaches...where have you gone??
entries.s_7: Hello? Oh, Mr. Love sent you? Thank the Force! I've lost my wonderful pet durni, Peaches. I can't stand it. Please help me find him.
